{"tid":2227349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方否認扣留希臘註冊貨輪 批評《蘋果》報道失實","createTime":"2020-10-02T16:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T01:08:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d4cc6708312ba158780d917a10168b1e7db6211d","tid":2227349,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:52:30.000Z","msg":"12 名港人上月底疑潛逃台灣時被中國海警截獲，遭扣押於深圳鹽田看守所已 41 日。《蘋果日報》今日報道，指近期連日出海、模擬 12 港人出航路線，發現曾有一艘遠洋貨輪與 12 港人在毗連區水域「擦身而過」，稱兩者僅相距約 2 公里，可能目擊 12 人被追截過程。報道指該希臘註冊貨輪現時停泊香港境內，並引述不具名外籍船員指該船「detained by police（遭警方拘留）」。<br />\n<br />\n警方今晚在 FB 發帖，否認扣留希臘註冊貨輪，不點名批評《蘋果》報道失實。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">根據《蘋果日報》報道，該報事先曾就事件向警方查詢，惟警方發言人拒絕以書面回覆，僅稱「冇聽過」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3517490785003183\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3517490785003183&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmbVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=34d40334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3517490785003183</a>"},{"pid":"81c63e14ae30f2edb9b4354ee5b6b088d096a94b","tid":2227349,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2298a6449b543347fb500ba67ef81231740ce86d","tid":2227349,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d811f819b7fac2346c129cffb83f79e88c313783","tid":2227349,"uid":273703,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1532c76b4e74d0b93fa93ab899e1ed1c745dcf31","tid":2227349,"uid":43062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"即係要繼續查落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/po